        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1818162381" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16169738957110740024">Another Remarque masterpiece, another strong female character who falls ill but most of all, another great story. Don&apos;t read this if you&apos;re looking for anything about Lisbon. The story follows a husband and wife as they flee Nazi Germany and seek refuge in America. The characters have serious depth and do everything they can just to survive. Some may think the wife&apos;s antics in the labour camp are a sign of weakness but if anything they lend her depth and complexity as a character. They also show</span>
  <span id="freeText16169738957110740024" style="display:none">Another Remarque masterpiece, another strong female character who falls ill but most of all, another great story. Don't read this if you're looking for anything about Lisbon. The story follows a husband and wife as they flee Nazi Germany and seek refuge in America. The characters have serious depth and do everything they can just to survive. Some may think the wife's antics in the labour camp are a sign of weakness but if anything they lend her depth and complexity as a character. They also show her will to live. This is a real love story not a soppy Nicholas Sparks kind of story. It shows what happens to love in the most dire of situations. Read this and then if you like it, read Flotsam.</span>
  <a data-text-id="16169738957110740024" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

